All Implemented Interfaces:
IHeap<E> 
public class BinomialHeap<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object

        implements IHeap<E>

Represents a Binomial Heap as linked list of Binomial Trees Each Tree is head ordered. Also, a proper Heap union ensures that B(k) appears in a n-node Heap if and only if k+1-th bit of binary representation of n is 1. This ensures O(lgn) number of trees.
